<para><bold>IADLXDisplaySettingsChangedEvent2</bold> is an extension interface to <ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_display_settings_changed_event" kindref="compound">IADLXDisplaySettingsChangedEvent</ref>, and provides methods to check for changes to the DCE settings.</para>
