</para>
<para>The <bold>IADLXDisplaySettingsChangedEvent2</bold> interface is obtained from the <ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_display_settings_changed_event" kindref="compound">IADLXDisplaySettingsChangedEvent</ref> interface or from any of its extension interfaces using <ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_interface__query_interface" kindref="compound">QueryInterface</ref>.</para>
